      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The control buttons allow you to re-import or find <text styleclass="SOLIDWORKS">SolidWorks</text> files if they are out-of-date.</para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Control Buttons: </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">Synch. all files :</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo2">&#32;</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Click <text styleclass="VariableName">Synch. all files </text>button to check you have the most up-to-date <text styleclass="SOLIDWORKS">SolidWorks</text> files.<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">The files import again, if needed.</para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Synchronize Selected Files: </para>
          <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text style="font-style:normal;">CTRL+Click</text> each <text styleclass="Element">CAD-Line</text>, in the Element Name list.<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Click <text styleclass="VariableName-indent">Synch. Selected Files</text>&#32;</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">MD will re-import the files again</para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Find Selected File: </para>
          <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click a </text><text styleclass="Element">CAD-Line</text> in the list<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Click <text styleclass="VariableName-indent">Find Selected File...</text> button</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-style:normal;">Browse to find a file</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> that </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MechDesigner</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> cannot find.</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
