          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The slider controls those <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">Affected Lights</text> that have a check in the check-box</para>
          <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click each <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">Affected Light</text> check-box to make lights active.<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="8" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Use the <text style="font-style:normal;">sliders</text> to change their<text styleclass="VariableName">: </text></li>
